E_D("replace into `new_ecms_news` values('47','33','0','0','0','0','2017-02-16','47','1','admin','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','1487227631','1487227631','1','0','0','','/en/programs/2017-02-16/47.html','1','1','1','','“New Perspectives” Award Ceremony','1487227591','','','The NPF will call for papers from scholars in universities, think tanks, and other research institutions across the U.S. in 2017. Paper topics will range from those pertaining to U.S.-China relations to broader subjects involving the Asia Pacific region.','0');");
